{center}
{subhead} Space Station 3000 Competition{def}
{left}
{p} {p}

 Digital Images have kindly given us two copies of their latest space
thriller game, Space Station 3000. It is a CD only game and requires
about 4mb Fast ram and 30mb HD space. To have the chance of winning
Space Station 3000, just answer this simple question :-
{p} {p}
Q:What is the closest star to Earth?
{p} {p}
Post off your answer to the usual email address : amiga@thefree.net
with the subject 'SS3000 Compo'
{p} {p}
--{p}
Competition Rules :
{p} {p}
 No members of the AIO editorial team or in anyway connected with AIO 
or Digital Images may enter. The Editors decision is final and no cash 
alternative will be offered.